lendent colors, beautiful hand-animated visuals, and a smooth, easy-listening soundtrack.\n\nAs a passionate artist, seek the missing colors that will bring your paintings to life - all while remembering to take the occasional coffee and breakfast breaks that keep you going. There is more than what meets the eye, for every painting has a story to tell.\n\nFeature List\n\u2022 Making Masterpieces: Paint, sketch, and retouch your artwork to complete your masterpiece and your memories\n\u2022 Intricate Immersion: Dive into and explore panoramic, VR worlds inspired by Miyazaki/Studio Ghibli visuals\n\u2022 Submerge in the Memory: Experience an evocative story, through the eyes of a passionate artist", "short_description": "Guide brush strokes and solve a variety of puzzles to help an aspiring artist complete her masterpiece amid her brusque neighbor\u2019s gaze and his pesky cat. As her painting starts to take shape, uncover an emotional tale of chance and artistry revealed behind unrelated yet familiar moments.\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.akuparagames.com/privacy-policy-of-behind-the-frame-the-finest-scenery-vr", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Akupara Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.akuparagames.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "961172191044986"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "fr", "it", "de", "es", "zh_TW", "zh_HK", "ru", "ja", "ko"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": 